title: Mindless Self Indulgence @ Electric Factory, Philadelphia, May 2
description:
This is Mindless Self Indulgence\&#039;s concert at the Electric Factory in Philadelphia, May 2nd, 2008.

This was filmed by me with a handheld video camera.  All song videos are in this file, with minimal breaks between videos (other than a major break between track 12 and 13, to switch camera batteries).  All are .MOV files.

Here\&#039;s the setlist for the night:
1 - Shut Me Up
2 - Mastermind
3 - Lights Out
4 - Stupid MF
5 - Issues
6 - 1989
7 - Never Wanted To Dance
8 - Prescription
9 - Revenge
10 - Animal
11 - Tornado
12 - Pay For It
13 - Faggot
14 - Capital P
15 - Evening Wear
16 - Bitches
17 - What Do They Know
18 - Planet Of The Apes
19 - Straight To Video
20 - I Hate Jimmy Page
